ALTER TABLE signal ADD AckTime datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00';
ALTER TABLE signal DROP GridCol;

CREATE TABLE sigbutdef(
  SigButDefNum smallint unsigned NOT NULL auto_increment,
  ButtonText varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  ButtonIndex tinyint unsigned NOT NULL,
  SynchIcon tinyint unsigned NOT NULL,
  ComputerName varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (SigButDefNum)
) DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE sigbutdefelement(
  ElementNum smallint unsigned NOT NULL auto_increment,
  SigButDefNum smallint unsigned NOT NULL,
  SigElementDefNum smallint unsigned NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (ElementNum)
) DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE sigelementdef(
  SigElementDefNum smallint unsigned NOT NULL auto_increment,
  LightRow tinyint unsigned NOT NULL,
  LightColor int NOT NULL,
  SigElementType tinyint unsigned NOT NULL,
  SigText varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  Sound text NOT NULL,
  ItemOrder tinyint unsigned NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (SigElementDefNum)
) DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE sigelement(
  SigElementNum mediumint unsigned NOT NULL auto_increment,
  SigElementDefNum smallint unsigned NOT NULL,
  SignalNum mediumint unsigned NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (SigElementNum),
  INDEX (SignalNum)
) DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
